
Requirements
Stock recovery.img (extracted from the firmware or by dumping the phone's ROM using Miracle Box, SP Flash tool etc )
Download MTK Auto Philz recovery porter by Team Hovatek from the link at the bottom of this post
Windows PC


STEPS:
Extract the MTK Auto Philz recovery porter zip
Copy the stock recovery.img into the stock folder
Double-click Auto Philz Recovery Porter.exe
Tap Enter to confirm that you've copied your stock recovery.img into the stock folder
Enter the option for your Android version (5 for Lollipop, 6 for Marshmallow & 7 for Nougat) and tap Enter
Type Y or N (depending on whether or not you have an external SD card in your phone) then tap Enter
Wait while our tool ports the Philz recovery
You'll find your ported Philz recovery in the output folder.
Flash the recovery image to your device



